## Next Steps for Deployment

To enable analytics data collection in production:
1. Deploy this application to Vercel
2. Navigate to your project dashboard on Vercel
3. Go to the Analytics section in the project sidebar
4. Click the "Enable" button in the header

Once enabled, the tracking script will automatically send visitor data to Vercel's analytics service on the next deployment.

